abstract: CÓDIGO DEL PROYECTO: 57204 — POR MARCHE FEDER 2014-2020 — EJE 3 — OS8 — ACCIÓN 8.2.ITI.AI — ESTRATEGIA NACIONAL ÁREAS INTERNAS — ALTA MACERACIÓN DEL ESPACIO INTERIOR Â LLAMADA PARA APOYAR LA COMPETITIVIDAD DE LAS EMPRESAS, A TRAVÉS DE INTERVENCIONES PARA CALIFICAR LA OFERTA Y LA INNOVACIÓN DE PRODUCTO/SERVICIO, TRAS LA EMERGENCIA COVID 19

motivations: The COVID-19 pandemic has negatively impacted the competitiveness of businesses, requiring interventions to enhance their product/service offerings and innovation.
objectives: Support the competitiveness of businesses by qualifying their product/service offerings and innovation capabilities in the aftermath of the COVID-19 pandemic.

motivations: The COVID-19 emergency has created challenges for business competitiveness that require targeted interventions.

objectives: Support business competitiveness through interventions that qualify product and service offerings.
Promote innovation in products and services in response to the COVID-19 emergency.
